12.short_description: TELL Toolkit creates speech and language protocols tailored to diverse disorders and research question.

The company's HIPAA-compliant SaaS solution is designed to address the challenges of early detection, specificity, cost, access, and reliability. By offering a unified, user-friendly, and scalable tool for discovering and implementing novel markers, we're bringing hope to patients, caregivers, and healthcare professionals across the globe.

So, whether you're a patient, physician, biotech company, health insurance provider, or government agency, TELL is here to help you make better decisions and improve brain health for all.

12.short_description: Clooned is a digital marketing tool that helps businesses to create 360-degree, 3D products and no-app required AR/VR experiences.

18.description:
3D is becoming a new media standard. And we believe that, it creates a new and fresh category in communication and marketing.

Clooned is an SaaS start up focused on the online capabilities of 3D files, for different needs such as sales, marketing, customer support and many more.
We specialize in creating web-based 3D technology, with a focus on sectors and today's needs.

With Clooned's online service, users can easily create a digital online copy of their 3D product models or spaces, and then use them in variety of ways, including on 360-degree web browser tours, in Augmented Reality (AR), and in Virtual Reality (VR).

One of the key benefits of Clooned's technology is that it eliminates the need for users to download a separate app in order to view 3D models on devices, also with AR or VR. Instead, users can simply access the models through a web browser, making it easy to share and collaborate on 3D projects with others.

Clooned's technology meets the diverse needs of a wide variety of industries, from maritime to defense industry, from architecture to machinery.
